#### QStash (by Upstash)

## QStash is a serverless messaging queueing and task scheduling solution. It fits easily into your existing workflow and allows you to build reliable systems without managing infrastructure.

# Main use is Background jobs, retries, webhook delivery and use HTTPS (push-based) protocol used

# Instead of calling an endpoint directly, QStash acts as a middleman between you and an API to guarantee delivery, perform automatic retries on failure, and more.

ðŸ“¬ What is QStash?
QStash is Upstash's serverless task queue that:

Sends HTTP POST requests to your endpoints at scheduled times

Includes retries, rate limiting, delay, deduplication

Great for background jobs and webhook orchestration

ðŸ“Œ Use cases:

Send transactional emails asynchronously

Retry failed webhooks

Delay notifications

Queue billing operations
